_sText:
Another armor prefab by me, this time it's the Soviet T80u Main Battle Tank.


This one was harder to replicate due to the odd turret shape and the amount of details.


2 versions included in the .vmf, one static and one with separate chassis and turret for posing purposes.


Also included is my crappy Soviet woodland camouflage, feel free to replace it or use it.


 If you use this prefab please give credit to me.
